China is to realize carbon neutrality by 2060. Huaneng Group, among China's biggest power generation companies, is one of the key players paving the way to achieving this goal. The smart and green initiative motivates power generation plants like Huaneng's to revolutionize away from traditional smokestack enterprises. Director&Reporter：Zhou Yiqiu Cameraman：Guo Yuanheng Video Editor：Zhou Yiqiu, Wang ZheExecutive Producer: Wang Mingyan Chief Editor：Zhang Wan